# CloudSentinelSuite

**Multi-Cloud Security Automation Framework** simulating real-world Security Engineer & Consultant responsibilities across AWS, Azure, and GCP.

---

## 🚀 Overview

CloudSentinelSuite is a hands-on, modular cloud security framework built to reflect enterprise-grade use cases across Identity, Network, Threat Detection, Compliance, and Automation.

It supports:
- Infrastructure as Code (Terraform)
- SIEM/SOAR integrations (AWS GuardDuty, CloudTrail, Sentinel)
- IAM governance & auto-remediation
- MITRE ATT&CK–based threat simulations
- Compliance-as-Code (AWS Config Rules + Lambda)

---

## 🧱 Modules

| Module                     | Description |
|----------------------------|-------------|
| `terraform/`               | Secure IaC modules for AWS, Azure, GCP |
| `iam-audit-remediation/`   | IAM misconfig analysis, auto-remediation scripts |
| `siem-sentinel/`           | CloudTrail + GuardDuty + EventBridge + Sentinel pipelines |
| `threat-simulation/`       | MITRE-based atomic tests using native and scripted events |
| `dashboards/`              | Security dashboards and visualizations |
| `encryption/`              | S3/KMS encryption policies and hardening tools |
| `auth-federation/`         | SAML-based SSO with Azure AD / Identity Center |
| `devsecops-pipeline/`      | tfsec + GitHub Actions for secure CI/CD |

